* [[Rome]], SkyBridge [[Leonardo da Vinci–Fiumicino Airport#SkyBridge|Leonardo da Vinci–Fiumicino Airport]]
* [[Milan]], MeLA: from [[Cascina Gobba (Milan Metro)|Cascina Gobba metro station]] to [[San Raffaele Hospital]]. 
* [[Pisa]], PisaMover: from [[Pisa International Airport]] to [[Pisa Centrale railway station]]. 
* [[Venice]], [[Venice People Mover]]: from [[Tronchetto|Tronchetto island]] to [[Piazzale Roma]]. 
* [[Bologna]], [[Marconi Express]]: from [[Bologna Guglielmo Marconi Airport]] to [[Bologna Centrale railway station]].

